sub_title: Inspector at Ministerie van Buitenlandse Zaken
summary:
My personal motto is: Kindness is no weakness, kindness makes you stronger. 
It is my purpose as an Ambassador to reach out to many, and to connect people that would not have met without me. 
People call me transparent, courageous, open and a leader who is approachable. I am not afraid to take risks and I am open to learn from my mistakes. 
I am an avid keynote speaker and many invite me to talk about my passion for sustainability, innovation, and cycling. I also focus on the power of vulnerability and how to avoid unconscious bias.
I always leave an organisation more diverse than I have found it when I started as a manager.
I am proud of the Dutch business community, as it is amongst one of the most innovative in the world. Innovation is a key driver for me as well. 
Presenting content is important. I invest in sustainable clothes, try to champion young designers and enjoy dressing up for special occasions.

I feel gratitude for life’s challenges, for helping me grow and for making me who I am today. 

via @MargrietVonno on twitter and Instagram I update my work experiences and travel.
